</taxonomicName>
can be readily distinguished from all its congeners by the following combination of characters: pelvic disc small (2.9­3.7 times in SL 
<emphasis box="[741,771,1334,1357]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">vs.</emphasis>
<quantity box="[129,243,1366,1389]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.62" metricValueMax="8.128" metricValueMin="7.111999999999999" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" unit="in" value="3.0" valueMax="3.2" valueMin="2.8">2.8­3.2 in</quantity>
